The '''Hanadaks''' were predatory [[Primate/Legends|primates]] indigenous to the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon]] of [[Endor (planet)/Legends|Endor]]. [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] have claimed that they were controlled by the [[Gorax/Legends|Gorax]], but none of them were able to prove this legend.<ref name="The Essential Guide to Alien Species" />

{{Creature-stub}}

==History==
One hanadak was responsible for killing [[Ra-Lee/Legends|Ra-Lee]], the mother of [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]], as well as separating [[Asha/Legends|Asha]] from Kneesaa and their father, [[Chirpa/Legends|Chirpa]], who presumed she was dead. In reality, Asha survived and had been adopted by [[Korrina/Legends|korrinas]]. She reunited with her father and sister years later.

Following the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the collector [[Jener Mich]] tasked a group of spacers to hunt and kill an unreasonable number of hanadaks.<ref name="SWG:HS">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=collection|Hanadak Slasher}}</ref>

